# fp-go monadic operations

Covers the core fp-go v2 combinators for building functional pipelines in Go:
`Pipe`/`Flow` arity matching, `E.Chain`/`E.Map`/`E.Fold` for Either, `IOE.Chain`
and `IOE.WithResource` for IOEither, `A.Chain`/`A.Flatten` for arrays, and
`R.Lookup`/`R.FromEntries` for records. Prefer data-last composition and keep
side effects isolated in IOEither.
